I"J<p>Basic Usage</p>

<p>Counters are initialized by data-attributes on page load.</p>

<p>Add the data-countup attribute to initialize the element as a counter.</p>

<p>By default, the counter will use the element’s text and count up to that value from zero. The text is parsed by the javascript parseFloat function, so you may use a decimal or integer.</p>

<p><span data-countup="">1234</span></p>

